      • AbstractAccountSyncedFieldImpl

        public AbstractAccountSyncedFieldImpl(java.lang.String baseFieldName)
        Handles access between an account-level entity's field that is associated with a policy-level (AccountSyncable) field. Utility constructor that assumes the account entity field name is the same as the baseFieldName, and that the policy entity field name is the baseFieldName + "Internal".
